RE: About Matthew 5:17 (Jesus said he has not come to change law) There is so much shit in that book. It's like telling one person a crazy miracle story, having him pass it on from memory to another person, who passes it on to another person, and so on two hundred times, then every fifth person writes down what they remembered, adding their own little tweaks as they do so. THEN that collection of scripts gets put together.
Hell, the original story doesn't even have to be that crazy at all, the amount of change is likely to make it insane.
Excellent way to find the truth about something, don't you all agree?
We are sceptical about rumours when they are told in this day and age, why not for one that was spread two thousand years ago?
